---
title: Spiced Chickpea & Kumara Buddha Bowl with Leafy Greens & Garlic Sauce
description: This bowl full of nourishment will leave you feeling satisfied and energised in equal measure. Between crunchy cabbage, roasted kumara and tasty chickpeas, every bite is a delight. Our favourite flourish is the dressing of rich garlic dip drizzled on top.
